The paper deals with a deep learning model for question-answering on scientific plots, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) tasks. Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also addresses reasoning and understanding, which are core topics in artificial intelligence (AI), making cs.AI another likely sub-category. The model is based on deep learning, which falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves language processing, which is a sub-topic of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
